{"tid":2262172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"栗戰書稱反對將病毒政治化污名化 譴責別國推卸責任","createTime":"2020-10-29T01:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T02:58:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"121b2423f90dd5afd87d6276f446cef6adae9784","tid":2262172,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國人大常委會委員長栗戰書表示，反對將新型冠狀病毒政治化和污名化。<br />\n<br />\n栗戰書出席金磚國家議會論壇視像會議指，中國今年首九個月國內生產總值增長0.7%，是疫情發生以來第一個實現正增長的主要經濟體，為世界經濟恢復貢獻了力量傳遞了信心。<br />\n<br />\n他建議，金磚國家立法機構加強公共衞生領域合作，為疫情防控提供法治保障，推進國際聯防聯控，反對將病毒政治化、污名化、標籤化，反對任意推責。<br />\n<br />\n栗戰書又指，要堅持開放創新發展，從法治的角度，維護以世貿組織為核心的多邊貿易體制，堅定維護國際法權威。"},{"pid":"ee312569311c5970a420a429a90fbc59fda53568","tid":2262172,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ae85ecec0238f17623ad4ed8c3fad6bc1398541","tid":2262172,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66593eb4c6ec174a9c653601dfb9a859f59536b4","tid":2262172,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:40:14.000Z","msg":"人地係幫你正名化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話明係中國武漢病毒"},{"pid":"c246e3da8cf16e2e3fe71946dd8d5b6062ae7cd2","tid":2262172,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"習近平D心腹都係冇乜讀過書既流氓 呢件栗戰書都算經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ab97f86b18c233633d3456692789071fbb1ad3","tid":2262172,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"自古以來，Covid-19都是中國武漢的"},{"pid":"d4817b1dff95769fbe7d209342e451e2f1ae0d91","tid":2262172,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc